sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI as amplihack CLI
    participant PluginCLI as plugin_cli/
    participant PluginMgr as PluginManager
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant Settings as settings.json

    User->>CLI: amplihack plugin install my-plugin
    CLI->>PluginCLI: plugin_install_command("my-plugin")
    PluginCLI->>PluginMgr: discover_plugin("my-plugin")
    PluginMgr->>FS: search known plugin directories
    FS-->>PluginMgr: plugin manifest found
    PluginMgr->>PluginMgr: validate plugin manifest
    PluginMgr->>FS: copy plugin files
    PluginMgr->>Settings: register in settings.json
    PluginMgr-->>PluginCLI: install complete
    PluginCLI-->>CLI: success
    CLI-->>User: "Plugin installed"
